description: Redevelopment of site involving the erection of a new seven storey building to provide 400m2 of floor space for purposes falling within Class A1 (Shops) and 200m2 of floor space falling within Class B1 (Business) of the Town and Country Planning (Use Classes) Order 2005 (as amended) at ground floor level together with six floors of residential units over comprising: fifty two 1-bedroomed, thirty nine 2-bedroomed and five 3-bedroomed self contained flats incorporating 38 affordable units and a landscaped courtyard. Provision of 94 car parking spaces at basement and ground levels (83 for residential use), 96 cycle spaces, refuse facilities, delivery and service area and vehicular access onto London Road.
